  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Shield the elderly from loneliness and isolation</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Covid-19 has hit the Halstead Day Centre hard.  The work of this much valued centre, which supports its members to enjoy Independent Living, is being frustrated by current restrictions of the pandemic. The number attending is now limited to 6, whilst the day to day running costs that ordinarily provide facilities for 20 members, remain much the same. Our aim is for the Centre to maintain the excellent service that it provides to the elderly people of Halstead and the surrounding villages.</narrative>
  </description>
